    <sidebar>
        <title>Project</title>

        <p>
            Mapcraft is a Java based tool for creating and managing maps
            for use in pen and paper roleplaying games. Maps are tile
            based, and make use of properties and meta data to keep track
            of objects and manage relationships between different maps.
        </p>
    </sidebar>

    <body>
        <sect1>
            <title>Current Features</title>
            
            <p>
                Supports hexagonal and square tiled maps.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Supports vectors for rivers and roads.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Supports free floating objects for towns and cities.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Xalan plugin for auto generating images from XML.
            </p>
        </sect1>
        
        <sect1>
            <title>Planned Features</title>
            
            <p>
                Automatically generate map statistics.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                GUI interface to merging of maps.
            </p>
        </sect1>
